type:workstation
name:Install nginx webserver
Installs an nginx webserver.

The `deploy-www` module in `data-workstation` automates deployment of static web content to a local nginx server. See README.md for more information.

The root nginx web content directory is: `/var/www/html`

The default URL is: [http://localhost/](http://localhost/)

To check the status of nginx:

```
$ sudo systemctl status nginx
