Set permissions on files in `/var/www/html/` as follows:

- Adds the current user (`$USER`) to group `www-data`
- Changes ownership for everything (recursively) in `/var/www/html` to `$USER:www-data`.

Incase of any issues with nginx, an error log is available:

```
$ tail /var/log/nginx/error.log
```

